-01-12T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"唔洗"},{"pid":"91609bab8231482fa961444ad60c5b97c101840a","tid":2363161,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:39:58.000Z","msg":"柒婆都話唔處理，牙姐組仲咁多意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162406be6e04e3a042c2050cb99687ec31fa756a","tid":2363161,"uid":121937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:40:50.000Z","msg":"不會影響現時持外國護照的人士。<br />\n<br />\n你咪好著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d56b5a46b9a0eed9977d6b8c203a4381949f68","tid":2363161,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:42:05.000Z","msg":"攬炒<br />\n英國國會收到!!"},{"pid":"9e8848d3e7c3d3f3e3ed852aede761e64083d79a","tid":2363161,"uid":18167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:42:45.000Z","msg":"葉劉好明顯想借搞BNO掃走晒777呢班高官啦 <br />\n<br />\n成個香港政府只係敢屌英國比BNO VISA<br />\n唔敢出聲搞BNO就係怕觸動中共神經<br />\n有係事上黎搞晒所有外國護照<br />\n而家葉劉不停吹話要中共禁雙重國籍<br />\n禁雙重國籍最大損失係班高官權貴<br />\n班高官權貴對中共黎講只係外人<br />\n會哄得掂中共唔理BC?<br />\n<br />\n禁雙重國籍可以幫葉劉掃走晒佢d政敵"},{"pid":"f3b2e0ff95010996a7168bd62339e5f6242484b8","tid":2363161,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"人大常委：屌你我自己都有外國國籍，你估我會唔會釋法"},{"pid":"7cb63d3e80f626c5c3d660f3d7b0184b17fc143d","tid":2363161,"uid":83344,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:46:09.000Z","msg":"點解唔影响現持有外國護照人士，有乜理據，佢地有特權？"},{"pid":"63c58bdcee4d4355e8ae5056e0eed0aa721a7376","tid":2363161,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a1d56b5a46b9a0eed9977d6b8c203a4381949f68","tid":2363161,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:42:05.000Z","msg":"攬炒<br />\n英國國會收到!!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"英國會否外交報